      "rationale": "Testing was conducted at a single load level (1500 N axial compression with 10 Nm bending moment) per the standard F1717 protocol. Absence of multi-condition testing prevents characterization of model accuracy across the full loading envelope. This factor is below the required level; the deficit is acknowledged and accepted given the regulatory standardization of the F1717 single-condition protocol."
