      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness and yield load are the primary regulatory endpoints for pedicle screw system 510(k) submissions. These quantities directly support the clinical claim of mechanical equivalence to predicate devices and are the outputs used in the intended model application."
