    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for model risk level 3. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) reflects the inherent constraint of the standardized ASTM F1717 single-condition protocol and is accepted on the basis that regulatory precedent establishes this protocol as sufficient for 510(k) mechanical equivalence demonstration. Overall credibility is judged sufficient to support the intended regulatory submission.",
